"data-caption=\"This is a caption\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            "
"<li><code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-caption=\"The Drupal Dance\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            <li><code>&lt;blockquote "
"data-caption=\"Dries Buytaert\"&gt;Drupal is "
"awesome!&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            "
"<li><code>&lt;code data-caption=\"Hello world in "
"JavaScript.\"&gt;alert(\"Hello world!\");&lt;/code&gt;</code></li>\n"
"  "
"      </ul>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Вы можаце дадаваць падпісы да "
"малюнкаў, відэа, цытат і г.д. "
"Прыклады:</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li><code>&lt;img src=\"\" "
"data-caption=\"Гэта падпіс\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    "
"<li><code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-caption=\"Танец Drupal\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    <li><code>&lt;blockquote "
"data-caption=\"Дрыс Буйтаерт\"&gt;Drupal — "
"выдатны!&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    "
"<li><code>&lt;code data-caption=\"Прывітанне, свет у "
"JavaScript.\"&gt;alert(\"Прывітанне, "
"свет!\");&lt;/code&gt;</code></li>\n"
"</ul>"

